This happens because the ciliary body, the lens, and the zonules work together.

00:02:20.800 --> 00:02:27.120
The ciliary body is joined to the choroid and is strongly connected to the sclera.

00:02:28.780 --> 00:02:33.520
The ciliary muscle is located inside the ciliary body. 

00:02:33.980 --> 00:02:37.000
This muscle can be tensioned or relaxed.

